      "file": "11-The Drawings of the Disadvantaged_ A Comparative Study.pdf",
      "title": "The Drawings of the Disadvantaged: A Comparative Study",
      "year": 1969,
      "doi": "10.1080/00393541.1969.11650656",
      "pageCount": 16,
