      "file": "14-The Arts _ Working Together to Make Education Work_ An Idea Whose Time Has Come.pdf",
      "title": "The Arts — Working Together to Make Education Work: An Idea Whose Time Has Come",
      "year": 1978,
      "doi": "10.1080/00393541.1978.11650207",
