      "file": "08-If and where to Plug in the Computer_ A Conceptual Framework for Computer Assisted Art Instruc.pdf",
      "title": "If and where to Plug in the Computer: A Conceptual Framework for Computer Assisted Art Instruction",
      "year": 1983,
