      "file": "13-A Comparative Study of Personality_ Values_ and Background Characteristics of Artistically Tal.pdf",
      "title": "A Comparative Study of Personality, Values, and Background Characteristics of Artistically Talented, Academically Talented, and Average 11th and 12th Grade Students",
      "year": 1988,
